EN: Xiaoming plays online games every day.

ZH: 她经常上网购物，花了很多钱。
EN: She often shops online and has spent a lot of money.

ZH: 上网速度很慢，我无法打开网页。
EN: The internet speed is slow, I can't open the webpage.

